---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="ostrom-score"
  description="Your Ostrom Score Self-Assessment Kit is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Ostrom Score is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your assessment"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Ostrom-Score-Self-Assessment-Kit-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>Eight principles from Nobel Prize-winning commons governance research. 32 diagnostic questions. Score your agent system against the structural conditions that cooperation requires.</p>
    <p>Most organizations score between 0 and 4 out of 24. The value is in the honesty, not the number.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/ostrom-score" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Score honestly</h3>
      <p>Score what exists in your architecture today. Not your roadmap. Not your intentions.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the score page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/level-6-governance-toolkit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Complete the audit</h3>
      <p>The Identity Violation Assessment and Agent Consent Architecture complete the Level 6 Governance Audit.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See the bundle &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/governance-audit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
      <p>If your score surfaces structural gaps, a Governance Diagnostic can help close them.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See audit options &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your results.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
